Body: Amazing project. Their token works on the NEO network. At their service, they accept 10 cryptocurrencies, but only not NEO. They consider NEO garbage and use the NEO blockchain. How do they do it ??

Author: Concierge.io
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: Hello. Thanks for your message and support of the project. We actually accept over 40 crypto currencies as payment via our payment partner Coingate. The reason NEO is not used as a payment option is because the token itself is not divisible meaning it can only be used in denominations of 1. Gas is the utility token of the NEO blockchain and is far more suited as a payment option. We will be adding payment in Gas to the platform soon.  Many thanks Steve

Body: https://medium.com/@travala/hello-traval-de6be673b1d  Update: Bitpaction Exchange Update  Dear Community,  We have been investigating the bitpaction issue by reaching out to their admin and until now we have had no response. We have had numerous complaints about the exchange and Bitpaction has not publicly addressed these issues raised by their users and based on this we recommend that any members of our community withdraw their AVA tokens from that exchange immediately.  We hope that Bitpaction release an update addressing the issues they have incurred, but until that time we urge extreme caution in dealing with that exchange.  As a general practice, we also recommend that you never store funds on an exchange, regardless of the size/reputation of it. The safest way to store cryptocurrency is in a wallet where you control the private keys; a hardware wallet is ideal.  Our partners at Switcheo decentralized exchange are trading AVA and we recommend use of their platform. We feel this is the best way for users to control their assets and keys to protect themselves.

Body: Leading Hotels on Travala.com On Wednesday the 18th July we will launch the next version of the platform which is the Travala Alpha V.2 Marketplace. In anticipation for this next release here are just some of the leading hotels of the world you will be able to book on the upcoming Travala platform at amazing prices.    What is Travala/AVA Travala is a decentralised Travel booking platform that leverages the power of the NEO blockchain and a zero-commission business model to provide cheap, seamless and safe hotel bookings.  You can play with the test site here: https://testnet.travala.com/ You can read up more about the project here: https://project.travala.com/ Or come talk to the friendly team over on Telegram here: https://t.me/travala  A Whole New World Blockchain technology may be synonymous only with cryptocurrency in many peoplesâ€™ minds, but it is increasingly being seen as a whole new way of building services across many industries.  The travel industry is ready for change and the Travala have the experience, know-how and crucially, the expertise within blockchain technology to come up with a platform that works for the end-user and the service provider and we are very excited to see our vision take even more steps forward on the 18th July. Author: Concierge.io
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: On May 8th, Concierge announced a rebrand to the name Travala, along with a planned migration from the domain concierge.io to travala.com. Travala is a travel booking marketplace on the NEO blockchain, aiming to be the first decentralized, trusted, zero commission travel platform.  In a post on the Travala subreddit addressed to the community, the Travala team stated that the rebrand is something they have given considerable thought to over a long period of time. Whilst operating under the name Concierge, they had tried to secure the concierge.com domain name which was not in use at the time. However, a â€œmulti-billion dollar companyâ€ was able to acquire the name first. This led the team to reconsider their branding, noting â€œTo move forward and become a truly global travel brand that would appeal to everyone, weâ€™ve always believed a .com was essential to that goal.â€  Travala was chosen as it is a â€œitâ€™s a unique and very travel-oriented, marketable brand that is easy for all nations and languages to useâ€, and the team have already started rebranding their social presence.  In addition, Travala will be changing their ticker symbol from CGE to AVA, and will be distributing AVA tokens to CGE holders at a ratio of 1:1. The total supply of AVA will be 61,571,086.  According to Travala, the AVA token will be listed on Switcheo soon after the distribution, allowing the team to keep its original promise of listing the token on an exchange within one month of the conclusion of the token sale.  Travala has warned users that there may be some downtime over the next few days whilst migration and testing is underway, but will provide more detailed updates as this occurs.  More information can be found at the link below â€“ https://www.reddit.com/r/Travala/comments/8hv5fa/conciergeio_rebrands_to_travalacom/

Author: Concierge.io
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: A Statement of Security regarding the Travala (AVA) NEP-5 Smart Contract  The recently identified â€œstorage injection vulnerabilityâ€ has impacted some NEP-5 based tokens. By exploiting this vulnerability, an attacker could alter the contract storage, causing varying degrees of damage. The story can be found here https://neo.org/blog/details/3080  Travala.com and the AVA NEP-5 token smart contract is unaffected by the storage injection vulnerability. As a result, AVA token holders are safe and sound and the above vulnerability has no impact to AVA holders.  Special thanks to Laurens and Chris over at Effect Ai for being such an amazing part of the NEO community.  The NEO organization and Red4Sec continue to go above and beyond to promote a healthy NEO ecosystem.  For more information on Travala.com, visit the following links: Medium: https://Travala.com Twitter: @travalacom Reddit: /r/travala Telegram: https://t.me/travala News & Updates: https://t.me/Travala_announcements

Author: Cryptocurrencies News
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: Project Exchange Strategy Update.  https://medium.com/@travala/project-exchange-strategy-update-acc0982f48cb  Itâ€™s been wonderful to see the excitement generated since Travalaâ€™s first exchange listing on Switcheo and weâ€™ve seen a great response in terms of AVAâ€™s recognition, growth, and positive performance especially when compared to the wider market.  Future exchange listings are just one of the many aspects weâ€™ve been strategically planning during Travalaâ€™s development. In fact, weâ€™ve been monitoring the performance of other project listings and been in discussions with our advisors. After exploring all the possible options available to us, weâ€™ve determined that listing on several smaller centralised and decentralised exchanges before building up to larger ones will likely help us achieve more stable growth.  By taking this approach, we can slowly but steadily build up liquidity and trade volume but also allow growth in different markets while we continue with the platform development. After all, our goal is to ensure Travala is a truly global brand.  Our preference is to build growth organically as weâ€™ve done so throughout our development and consistently build knowledge of Travala in the market so that we donâ€™t hit a large exchange, get traded for a few days and then forgotten again. We will also have our rebranded and upgraded platform back up and running again and rest assured a large exchange listing will come around the same time along with a solid awareness campaign. We realise that this may not be what is considered â€˜normalâ€™ for many other crypto listings however this model will ensure more stable, sustainable and steady growth for Travala and our precious AVA token.  We are pleased to announce not just one, but two exchange listings. The first listing on June 7th is Bitpaction.com and that will open up the first BTC/AVA and ETH/AVA pairings. There will be a number of competitions within the exchange, these details are TBA.     ANN: https://support.bitpaction.com/hc/en-us/articles/360005283414-Travala-AVA-WILL-GET-LISTED-ON-BITPACTION  There is a second listing coming within the next month, exact date and which exchange will be released in due course.

Author: Concierge.io
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: On March 23rd, Concierge.io, a travel booking marketplace on the NEO blockchain, launched its alpha platform in the lead up to their CGE token sale on March 31st.  The platform can be accessed at www.concierge.io.  As the product is in alpha, there are a limited number of available properties and platform functions, with new functions on their way. At present, users can only search for properties in Vietnam. When placing a booking, there is a 12 hour cooling off period for extra peace of mind. After the 12 hour cooling off period, bookings are non-refundable.  Features of Concierge.io Features of Concierge.ioâ€™s travel booking marketplace are below:  Customers can book using CGE tokens, Concierge.ioâ€™s native currency. Customers can log in with their Facebook or Google account once registered. However, customers must first create an account before logging in with Google or Facebook. Payment initiates via smart contracts, in-line with the 12-hour cooling-off period. One room bookings are available for each property with instant reservations. Concierge.io have stated that new functions are on their way. The new features are due for the beta release at the end of Q2 2018, as per Conciergeâ€™s roadmap. An update on progress will be provided at the conclusion of the token sale, starting on the 31st of March 9:00am UTC, ending the 28th of April.  Until then, users can report bugs for its alpha platform using this link.  Concierge.io Token Sale Event The token sale event has a hard cap of 45 million CGE tokens, with 1 CGE equal to USD 0.35. Payment for CGE tokens can be made in NEO tokens only, with a 1 NEO minimum and 250 NEO maximum.  The funds from the token sale will go towards the development of its CGE booking ledger, the core of Concierge.ioâ€™s ecosystem. Besides bookings, the CGE booking ledger also supports direct communication between customers and merchants, with 0% commissions taken by Concierge.io. In total, 100 million CGE tokens will be minted, with 65% allocated to the public for token sale events.  https://neonewstoday.com/general/concierge-io-alpha-booking-platform/

Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: Every booking made on the platform will use the CGE token. If a user pays with fiat or any other crypto then CGE will be purchased and used for the booking. After checkout the CGE will be released to the vendor where they can be paid out in Fiat or CGE. CGE will also be what is used for referral payments, loyalty and rewards. Featured advertising will be paid for in CGE. So there is constant buying pressure for the token. Also a lot of CGE will be locked in the smart booking contracts which will decrease availability. So all functions happening in the background will utilise the CGE token.  Here are some of the main advantages of concierge                    a. 0% Commission model to the suppliers as opposed to 15% to 45% with other OTAs. Savings will be passed onto the customer in the cheaper prices and increased service.                                            b. Peer to Peer communication between customer and supplier    c. automated disputes carried out by the smart contract.                        d. Immutable Reviews that can not be manipulated                              e. CGE loyalty and Rewards program.                                              f. Multiple payment options - Fiat, CGE and Other top crypto currencies

Author: Concierge.io
Title: ğŸš€ğŸ”¥[NEO][ANN]ğŸ”¥Travala.com - Travel Booking Marketplace built on NEOğŸš€
Body: Travala    About Travala.com  Travala.com (AVA) is a travel booking platform based on the NEO blockchain. The platform itself operates both a centralised front-end allowing suppliers to easily edit their listings, whilst operating a decentralised backend incorporating the NEO blockchain governing the AVA engine. Thus, building a trusted, transparent and secure travel booking platform reducing costs associated with the travel industry.  AVA aims to disrupt the travel industry and provides multiple benefits over potential competitors within the market. A free business model, 0% booking and commission fees for the suppliers with no hidden fees. The incorporation of a peer-to-peer chat function between supplier and consumer along with ability to pay with AVA, other crypto and Fiat-currency payment options. Furthermore, potential competition within the blockchain travel space typically utilising the Ethereum blockchain which operates the proof-of-work protocol. Currently, this does not provide scalability for a travel booking platform [with only 15 Transactions per second]. High transaction costs powered by a mining network contributing to the unsustainable developments of this particular blockchain on both an economic and environmental level. Thus, does not offer many benefits for a real-life use case.  Travala.com was designed to be a real-world use platform and by utilising the NEO blockchain it allows us to position ourselves above potential competition operating within the crypto space. NEO operating at 1,000 transactions per second with the aim to be running at 100,000 TPS by 2020 [as mentioned in NEO Devcon]. With the current speed of a transaction taking approximately 30 seconds to complete, which is something, a travel booking platform needs to consider competing against market leaders such as booking.com, KAYAK, Expedia.com, Viator or agoda.com. Costs per transaction cost just a drop of gas [less Thant $0.001]. NEO offers an eco-friendly approach by utilising the proof-of-stake protocol. Furthermore, eliminating any associated economical and environment issues associated with other blockchains. NEO consensus offers government compliance which Travala.com will incorporate once we begin advancements in new and emerging markets and regions across the globe.  AVA token system encourages and supports multiple scenarios such as smart contracts, exchange of data, booking agreement and dispute mechanism. In addition, the AVA infrastructure supports the development and mapping of the dApp and HTML web platform enabling Travala.com to reach the mass consumer within the travel industry.
